1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about deliberate practice than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:07,200
Deliberate practice isn't just about repetition.

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:09,600
It's a focused way to improve.

4
00:00:09,600 --> 00:00:13,600
Think of it as setting specific goals and receiving feedback.

5
00:00:13,600 --> 00:00:14,800
That's the key!

6
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:17,600
Research shows that just practicing isn’t enough.

7
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:20,400
It's the quality of practice that matters.

8
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:26,400
So, next time you pick up a skill, remember: deliberate practice can transform your abilities.

9
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:30,000
Want to dive deeper into the science of learning?

